file.name: OpenApi_defn_not_schema.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /pets:
    patch:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PetByType'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Updated
    get:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PetByAge'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Updated

components:
  schemas:          
    PetByType:
      type: object
      properties:
        pet_type:
          not:
            type: integer
      required:
        - pet_type

    PetByAge:
      type: object
      properties: 
        age:
          not:
            type: string
        nickname: 
          type: string
      required:
        - age
